In this Oval Office meeting, President Biden expresses gratitude for the support of the American people in passing the American Rescue Plan. He views this legislation as historic and essential for rebuilding the country's foundation and providing working people and the middle class with a better future. The President plans to address the nation and answer questions about the bill in the coming days. He signs the bill during the meeting and mentions upcoming opportunities to discuss its impact on ending the pandemic and other aspects of the legislation.